# MkDocs documentation

When you change public exports under `src/ianuacare/`, behavior of `Pipeline` / `Orchestrator` / `InputDataParser` / `OutputDataParser`, or AI inference wiring, update the relevant pages under `docs/` (see `mkdocs.yml` `nav`) in the **same change set**.

Before finishing: run `mkdocs build --strict` from the repo root and fix any warnings or broken links.
